.TH SHOAL-TOKEN 1 "July 2026" "Shoal 0.1.0" "User Commands"
.SH NAME
shoal-token \- manage Shoal capability tokens
.SH SYNOPSIS
.B shoal-token create
.I principal
.RI [ profile ]
.RI [ \-\-cap " cap" ]
.RI [ \-\-ttl " seconds" ]
.br
.B shoal-token list
.br
.B shoal-token revoke
.I id
.SH DESCRIPTION
Creates, lists, and revokes credentials used to authenticate kernel clients.
.SH ENVIRONMENT
.TP
.B SHOAL_TOKEN_STORE
Override the token database path.
.SH SEE ALSO
.BR shoal-mcp (1),
.BR shoal-kernel (1)
